involves Dr. Jiang.

23
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,680
Of course, I should come to him.

24
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,360
What?

25
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,280
Well,

26
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:55,080
the one who reported her
anonymously was you, right?

27
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,200
This...

28
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,880
Since we're on the subject,

29
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,280
let's make it clear.

30
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,720
Meng Yingchao,

31
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,520
because of your possessiveness,

32
