37
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,040
What do you really want to do?

38
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:25,480
This...

39
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,480
It's not him. It is...

40
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,000
Who is it?

41
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,960
Anyway, don't talk nonsense.

42
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,480
I just saw you two
being intimate right here.

43
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,640
I wanted to save you some face
in front of these people around,

44
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,360
but you've gone too far.

45
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,360
Meng Yingchao,

46
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,560
is the gin good?

47
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,720
Didn't you say
that he acted like you very well?

48
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,960
Didn't you say you wanted
to give him your marriage?

49
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,160
Let's get a divorce.

50
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,400
For the sake of the baby,

51
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,400
just forgive him once.

52
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,800
Forgive him?

53
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,200
Then who'll compensate for my marriage,

54
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,480
