55
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,720
The baby is innocent.

56
00:03:47,885 --> 00:03:50,304
(Kanglan People's Hospital Lab Results:
Negative, Not Pregnant)

57
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,080
There isn't a baby at all.

58
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,880
If not, would she go to see you?

59
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,160
Would you go home?

60
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,160
Mom.

61
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,680
You are uniting to trap me up.

62
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,520
To first ruin my reputation,

63
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:08,120
and now you are forcing me
to divorce, aren't you?

64
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,880
Meng Yingchao, you've had enough.

65
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:12,880
Just because Weiqi doesn't say anything,
you think she's easy to bully?

66
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,000
You are the many,

67
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,720
banding together to pick on us.

68
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:19,720
You are too cruel.

69
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:21,640
You lied to us about being pregnant.

70
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,960
Now you are banding
together to trick us.

71
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,640
He is 30 years old,

72
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,360
but he can't even feed himself

73
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,440
or wash his own underwear.

74
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:30,040
Your indulgence made him the man he is.

75
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,280
Weiqi.

76
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,280
Yingchao.

77
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,120
Stay away.

78
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,160
Everyone get out!

79
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,320
Yingchao.

80
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,640
Yingchao.

81
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,840
Yingchao.

82
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,440
Don't stop me.

83
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,880
Yingchao.

84
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,800
What do you want?

85
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,000
What do I want?

86
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,600
What do you want?

87
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,760
This is what you want, isn't it?

88
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,840
You're driving me crazy.

89
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,040
You're trying
to drive me crazy, aren't you?

90
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:01,440
Yingchao, don't be rash.

91
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,040
Meng Yingchao,

92
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,600
I know all about you
going to the New Club.

93
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:11,160
You planted a fake one by my side
and you have the nerve to say

94
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,440
all of this was caused by me!

95
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,600
Even if all of this is my fault,

96
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,120
can't you just talk nicely to me?

97
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,280
Do you have to make
such a fuss about this?

98
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,800
Are you happy to see this mess now?

99
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,400
Hello.

100
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,680
Is this a mental hospital?

101
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,280
There's a mental patient
making a scene here.

102
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,120
Someone's gonna get hurt soon.

103
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,840
At Yameijia Clinic.

104
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,200
In the corridor outside,

105
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,840
I lost my first child.

106
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:43,720
I didn't go abroad
for the sake of our relationship.

107
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,000
And you?

108
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,920
Three days after my miscarriage,
you were with Shi

109
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,840
in a bar, holding hands
with a strange woman.

110
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,640
Mr. Sheng, please wait.

111
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,720
How is it? Is the child okay?

112
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,000
You know I have hemophobia.

113
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,000
I can't be of any use here.

114
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,600
Mom has made chicken soup at home.

115
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,480
You should take a good rest.

116
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,560
I have a meeting to attend.

117
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,880
You don't remember, do you?

118
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,320
I really regret it.

119
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,360
I regret not exposing you.

120
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:15,760
Let's divorce

121
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,320
and make all of this public.

122
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,240
The last seven years

123
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,280
were one big farce.

124
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:28,640
No.

125
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,680
I will not divorce you.

126
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,400
If you make it hard for me,

127
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,280
