132
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,280
Go in. What are you doing?

133
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,960
Stop taking photos.

134
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,240
Yingchao.

135
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,360
Yingchao.

136
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,440
Yingchao.

137
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,760
Yingchao.

138
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,600
Severe paranoid personality disorder.

139
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,960
Distorting facts
and starting having delusions.

140
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,280
Suspecting his spouse
of being unfaithful.

141
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,480
Attacking and monitoring his spouse.

142
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,200
Even showing violent
and aggressive behavior.

143
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:21,920
Take him away now.

144
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,840
Yingchao.

145
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:35,160
Meng Yingchao is really odious.

146
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:38,160
