153
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,720
He is not Meng Yingchao.

154
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,760
You are not Meng Yingchao?

155
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,680
I want to talk to my wife

156
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,600
