157
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,760
First, she is not your wife.

158
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:11,640
Second,

159
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,760
we don't think it's safe
for her to be alone with you.

160
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,480
So we'll talk here

161
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,520
or at home?

162
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,400
I'll go home with you.

163
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,440
Weiqi.

164
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:22,320
Don't worry.

165
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,000
Let's go.
